{"tid":387302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"橋本環奈自拍特寫照 網友放大瞳孔驚叫「那是我家」","createTime":"2017-09-04T13:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T05:17:18.000Z","uid":9573,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"481d54480793c319189b50e78b117d74db18f47a","tid":387302,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2768/d2768523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2768%2Fd2768523.jpg&h=53bec1ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈自拍美瞳，網友發現驚人真相。<br />\n<br />\n日本女星橋本環奈被封為「千年難得一見美少女」，最近演出電影《銀魂》和日劇《警視廳生物課》人氣再飆。她在日劇裡扮演女警，嬌小身材穿上藍制服，宛若COSPLAY的型十分吸睛，最新一集找來貓頭鷹共演，學動物表情近距離自拍，意外引起驚人發現！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2768/d2768524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2768%2Fd2768524.jpg&h=597bc8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼橋本環奈主演《警視廳生物課》飆人氣，還模仿貓頭鷹自拍高清美瞳。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2768/d2768520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2768%2Fd2768520.jpg&h=dd31c64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈見到貓頭鷹十分興奮，和貓頭鷹一起拍照、錄宣傳影片，被觀眾狂讚「萌翻啦」、「超可愛！」她模仿貓頭鷹眼神，近距離自拍眼睛，澄明大眼被讚電力破表，還有人不斷放大後，美瞳裡反光映出高樓建築，這時居然有位男網友留言驚叫：「環奈瞳孔裡的大樓是我家！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2768/e2768528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2768%2Fe2768528.jpg&h=b72f0612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2768/d2768520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2768%2Fd2768520.jpg&h=dd31c64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友在橋本環奈的瞳孔裡看到自己家，引來眾人好奇，還有人問到他能否取代尼馬，迪比利立即說不可能：忍不住說「好恐怖。」粉絲同時注意到偶像肌膚緊緻，近距離拍攝幾乎沒有毛細孔，再加上迷人的逆天睫毛，狂讚「超級可愛」、「妳是No.1」、「美麗的眼睛！」"},{"pid":"85ffea7233b6a9f04565f2d162f5e09cb3c3dddb","tid":387302,"uid":91631,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"還有人問到他能否取代尼馬，迪比利立即說不可能<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8249aa2b9012c7b54b803ab072cc942cb19b18","tid":387302,"uid":119230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"個網友就係迪比利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba88f19ad5a523578f3685c4034d52efc480222e","tid":387302,"uid":139042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fd387d84ccf405c3e53b064f25af0a3edec206","tid":387302,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"唯口土"},{"pid":"8cd4f899820c830a6d0b3d1527a1f36d1ef6bac3","tid":387302,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯唯</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0f0982443722de0c710cf9ed003d96710396f71","tid":387302,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5e9f364ba9d0614b20c5b0abea4680dca5f1c8","tid":387302,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5106c409c47604e62c2b79f69828ae0d625d1cf4","tid":387302,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"橋本巧正"},{"pid":"a68c7b27cf05a0e1051efef124d47e67ba0931df","tid":387302,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5092a9ac4ee86a12ef7b94dee19e00b11459bf77","tid":387302,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:18:15.000Z","m